3070
01:29:27,200 --> 01:29:30,120
We have to look out for ourselves
and those around us.

3071
01:29:30,120 --> 01:29:31,680
In today's story,

3072
01:29:31,680 --> 01:29:34,360
Tui Nengzao faked a video
